attributes.action: Drivers who hit cats in their car should stop and take the cat to a vet
attributes.additional_details: As my cat was knocked over 2 months ago. If the person behind didn't stop he could have died.
attributes.background: To change the law: require drivers who accidently hit a cat in their car to stop and take the cat to the vet.
